{fork, spoon, knife, napkin}
{wood, metal}
{surface, supports}
{idea{implements}}
{form, matter}
{planes{lines{points}}}
{ourselves{our hands{our heads}}}
{all meals held at this table}
{micro-organisms}
{ideology}
{an impression}
{trust}
{handprints}
{ }

You consider taking { }, then [[remember|dining room][$table = true, $inthishouse = true]] you have one in your breast pocket.

